msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "The Pope on AI—Too Much Power in Too Few Hands"
msgstr "El Papa respecto a la IA: demasiado poder en muy pocas manos"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid ""
"In this letter, Mozilla Foundation Executive Director Nabiha Syed reflects on her meeting with Pope Leo XIV and why openness—open code, open governance, and open doors—is essential to building a "
"better, more ethical AI future where everyone can imagine, create, and participate in what comes next."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "title"
msgid "The Pope on AI—Too Much Power in Too Few Hands"
msgstr "El Papa respecto a la IA: demasiado poder en muy pocas manos"

